A

1.11.3. Standards

6.6kV switchgears shall be designed, manufactured, and tested under the following

applicable standards:

IEC 62271-200-MV 2 Metal-Clad Switchgear

IEC General 60694 Application

IEC 62271-Circuit 100 Breakers

IEC 62271-Earthing 102 Switches

IEC 60071-Coordination 2 of The Insulation

IEC Protection 60282 fuses

IEC 61869-Current 2 Transformers

IEC 61869-Voltage 3 Transformers

IEC Protection 60255 Relay

IEC Classification 60529 of Degree Protection

IEC 60099-Surge 4 Arrester

